{"tid":1369890,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唉 痴線 完全訓唔著 明明已經發過好多次夢","createTime":"2019-07-26T22:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T19:39:32.000Z","uid":95803,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dd315a065922a687b901e4f22b961a3b5bfe651d","tid":1369890,"uid":95803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:12:12.000Z","msg":"六點都過埋 明明已經發過好多次夢<br />\n前線 中排 後援 都發過<br />\n椒水食過 催淚又中過<br />\n其實已經無乜再可以驚 但唔知點解就係訓唔到<br />\n各位同路人 聽日一切小心 齊裝備 <br />\n呢個副本唔易打 我地要一齊黎 一齊走 <br />\n可以去到呢一刻我地真係好勁 更加不能放棄<br />\n但我真係完全無諗過 真係好滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\neven好開心自己有份同大家一齊堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有呢個機會同大家一齊奮鬥 係我既榮幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 想同男朋友講 我知你有上連登 有緣就見到 <br />\n不過俾你見到又係會開住個po黎笑9 me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我無怪過你無陪我發夢 我知你跑得耐會腳痛 <br />\n可能痛起上黎行都行唔到 驚怕連累我<br />\n所以我一直都無嬲你 知嗎？<br />\n你知你女朋友我係衝動派 係痴線婆 係政治撚 <br />\nig story全部都係有關發夢既事<br />\n仲要一嬲起上黎唔理3721就爆 拉都拉唔住<br />\n真係Exact7ly男仔性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有時我都諗唔明點解你會揀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住阿 呢排我地見面我就捉住你係咁講發夢<br />\n好似無點樣同你傾過計 多謝你體諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後既日子 我會盡我能力去對你好<br />\n我好想追返我同你認識之前既歲月<br />\n要創造好多好多好多好多既回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到尾 我都係想你心只屬於我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我都係 都係得你一個 無其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愛你bobo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b61d605a15cb17184cf43000844c46d333623c","tid":1369890,"uid":135461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:16:26.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"e00e7f64e52af2be3b1430f9c839ea942e321488","tid":1369890,"uid":82829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:17:27.000Z","msg":"男友：noted with thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講笑 好難得你可以咁體諒對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a8ad83a6f84073c7fca499787217137a163b3f","tid":1369890,"uid":95803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73b61d605a15cb17184cf43000844c46d333623c","tid":1369890,"uid":135461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:16:26.000Z","msg":"加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:21:57.000Z","msg":"謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b503173a7192798d9825a27e27bfb4d5a05f9a2c","tid":1369890,"uid":95803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e00e7f64e52af2be3b1430f9c839ea942e321488","tid":1369890,"uid":82829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:17:27.000Z","msg":"男友：noted with thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講笑 好難得你可以咁體諒對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T22:23:07.000Z","msg":"哈哈 可能佢訓醒都會咁答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggr